        "summary": {
          "diffs": [
            {
              "file": "bench-artifacts/cache-api.md",
              "patch": "Index: bench-artifacts/cache-api.md\n===================================================================\n--- bench-artifacts/cache-api.md\t\n+++ bench-artifacts/cache-api.md\t\n@@ -0,0 +1,55 @@\n+# Cache API\n+\n+Exported from `bench-targets/docs/src/cache.mjs`\n+\n+## createCache()\n+\n+Creates and returns a cache instance with `get`, `set`, `delete`, and `clear` methods.\n+\n+### Parameters\n+\n+None.\n+\n+### Returns\n+\n+Returns a cache object with:\n+\n+- **get(key)** - Gets the value associated with the given key. Returns `undefined` if the key is not found.\n+- **set(key, value)** - Sets the value for the given key. Returns the provided value.\n+- **delete(key)** - Deletes the value associated with the given key. Returns `true` if the key existed, `false` otherwise.\n+- **clear()** - Clears all entries from the cache by clearing the internal `Map`.\n+\n+### Example\n+\n+```js\n+import { createCache } from './cache.mjs'\n+\n+const cache = createCache()\n+cache.set('key1', 'value1')\n+cache.set('key2', 'value2')\n+const value1 = cache.get('key1') // 'value1'\n+cache.delete('key2')\n+cache.clear()\n+```\n+\n+## Methods\n+\n+### createCache()\n+\n+Exports from the module. Returns a cache instance.\n+\n+### get(key)\n+\n+Gets the cached value for the given key.\n+\n+### set(key, value)\n+\n+Sets a value in the cache for the given key. Returns the stored value.\n+\n+### delete(key)\n+\n+Removes the entry for the given key from the cache.\n+\n+### clear()\n+\n+Removes all entries from the cache.\n",
              "additions": 55,
              "deletions": 0,
              "status": "added"
            }
          ]
        },
        "id": "msg_ee4ec4fa9001qQF4NSeV7jTg0y",
